        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Undercutting</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">If the Cam&apos;s <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Radius-of-Curvature</text> is negative, and is less than the Radius of the Cam-Follower, then undercutting will occur.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="margin-left:24px;"><text style="font-size:12pt;">| ρ</text><text style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:sub;">cam </text>| <text style="font-size:12pt;">&lt;</text>&#32;<text style="font-size:12pt;">R</text>&#32;<text style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:sub;">cam-follower</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Do one or all of :: </para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">reduce the size of the Cam-Roller </li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">edit the motion to reduce the cam-follower velocity, </li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">increase the size of the cam</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">find another way to improve the transmission between the cam and the cam-follower.</li>
          </list>
        </td>
